此地下車站在1933年8月19日啟用<ref name=NYTimes-INDQBLCrstwnOpen-1933>{{cite web|title=TWO SUBWAY UNITS OPEN AT MIDNIGHT; Links in City-Owned System in Queens and Brooklyn to Have 15 Stations.|url=https://query.nytimes.com/mem/archive/pdf?res=9E0CEFDE1231EF3ABC4052DFBE668388629EDE|publisher=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|accessdate=November 7, 2015|date=August 18, 1933}}</ref>，設有兩個[[側式月台|側式月台]]和兩條軌道<ref name=MTA-GLineReview-Append-2013>{{cite web|title=Review of the G Line: Appendices|url=http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/G_Appendices_7_10_13.pdf|publisher=[[Metropolitan_Transportation_Authority|Metropolitan Transportation Authority]]|accessdate=October 28, 2015|date=July 10, 2013|archive-date=2016-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160127233038/http://web.mta.info/nyct/service/G_Appendices_7_10_13.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

此站是IND跨城線在布魯克林的最北端車站。最往北，路線將下穿{{link-en|新鎮溪|Newtown Creek}}進入[[皇后區|皇后區]][[長島市|長島市]]。
